schools.name: Palm Bay Magnet Senior High School

data.description: Perfectly situated on a quiet street in Palm Bay, this home has a lot to offer! Summers can be spent in the pool, recently converted to salt water for low maintenance care, and screened in too! For those few cold Florida winter days, dinner by the fire place is the perfect way to unwind. NEW ROOF in 2023 and A/C in 2022. Updated flooring and baseboard. Updated light fixtures. Updated bathrooms. And you can't miss the air conditioned garage with epoxied floors. Walking distance to Turkey Creek Trail! This one is a must see.
